-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Apache Parquet format
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
nanoarrow2parquet is an independent C++ implementation of a minimal Apache
Parquet writer. It does NOT link the Parquet reference implementation; it writes
the format directly. Its Thrift field ids and enum values are derived from the
Apache Parquet `parquet.thrift` definition:

    Apache Parquet — https://github.com/apache/parquet-format
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

